09:05.320 --> 09:07.680
Yeah. Nice man. Thank you...

09:07.680 --> 09:09.200
now where was I?

09:09.200 --> 09:11.400
Oh, yes, Maria's wedding.

09:11.400 --> 09:15.800
And Dermot's.
She's not marrying herself!

09:15.800 --> 09:20.520
Yes, of course. I just
wanted to have a little chat...

09:20.520 --> 09:22.840
make sure we don't clash on the day.

09:22.840 --> 09:24.560
You and me clash? Not at all.

09:24.560 --> 09:26.440
You keep your fuckin' mouth shut,
we'll be grand.

09:26.440 --> 09:27.880
DOOR CLOSES

09:30.760 --> 09:33.960
Betty? Betty?

09:34.520 --> 09:37.640
What do you want?
Is my husband here?

09:37.640 --> 09:39.360
Betty, I wish you'd use his name.

09:39.360 --> 09:41.360
Mark... Ma-ha-hark..

09:41.360 --> 09:45.000
