11:49.320 --> 11:51.040
Tea? Cup of tea?

11:54.960 --> 11:57.440
Er, yes, yes... No, no.

11:57.440 --> 12:02.640
Um, look, my outfit for the wedding.
I've had it put by at Harvey Nicks.

12:02.640 --> 12:05.400
